{"tid":786791,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[唔準笑]李克強稱難以想像有國家單獨建防火牆","createTime":"2018-08-20T07:42:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-20T10:00:15.000Z","uid":156363,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"7762f00e6487fb0e7b1d69f09880f85aceb659dc","tid":786791,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T07:42:09.000Z","msg":"正在訪華的馬來西亞總理馬哈蒂爾，在人民大會堂與總理李克強會面，兩人其後共同會見記者。<br />\n<br />\n對於中美貿易戰，李克強重申貿易戰沒有贏家，貿易摩擦發生後，短期內會為部分國家帶來替代效應，但從長遠來看，將衝擊貿易體系、惡化自由貿易、帶來的負面衝擊明顯。他舉例指，若一條河的水質惡化，帶來的負面衝擊並不只涉及河裡生存的數種魚，而是有可能所有生物均受到衝擊、生存環境有可能惡化，所以很難想像有國家單獨興建一道防火牆。<br />\n<br />\n馬哈蒂爾說，自由貿易是正確的方式，但認為同時需要公平貿易，因為不同國家的發展水平不同，因為窮國與富國的競爭很難，所以不僅要開放的貿易，也要是公平的貿易。"},{"pid":"7906c22a09218038fe7c1f19b1e3776cf5012e65","tid":786791,"uid":14918,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T07:44:24.000Z","msg":"唔笑果下勁"},{"pid":"127e9ce51bde3c251bdc8667e653f8c2a1b7d1b8","tid":786791,"uid":156363,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"7906c22a09218038fe7c1f19b1e3776cf5012e65","tid":786791,"uid":14918,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T07:44:24.000Z","msg":"唔笑果下勁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T07:50:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/20/155004_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F20%2F155004_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=2712f799&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9f2d26eb62f8088a3bb071e7806fa9bb79c90f57","tid":786791,"uid":155095,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T07:50:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-YxXUyRBe6oQ/WTOin99I0LI/AAAAAAAAQV4/xIeFuON5JmMwR8s4AxrnRTGokFGq_7U_QCLcB/s1600/firewall_china.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-YxXUyRBe6oQ%2FWTOin99I0LI%2FAAAAAAAAQV4%2FxIeFuON5JmMwR8s4AxrnRTGokFGq_7U_QCLcB%2Fs1600%2Ffirewall_china.jpg&h=3f35c604